tic tac toe
two players -  x and o
on a 3 x 3  grid 
if player gets 3 x or o, the player wins the game ends and starts again

  o |   |
-------------
    | o | x
-------------
    |   | o

on a 3 x 3 grid

when the user clicks any box,  a "x" appears 

right after the next turn when a box is clicked a "o" will appear

this in intervals until 3 "x" or "o" appears 

    which a line crosses the 3 "x" or "o"

    game ends

or  the grid is filled - a draw 
    game ends



